<% partial 'partials/material_sub_heading' do %>
    Getting a TMC account
<% end %>

<p>
    You need an account for University of Helsinki's TMC system (you don't need to be a student at the University, if you are remember to put in your student number). You'll use it to log into both the TMC plugin in Qt Creator, and to this course material site to submit feedback and peer-review exercises. You can also view your TMC submissions at the <a href="https://tmc.mooc.fi">TMC website</a>. Head on <a href="https://tmc.mooc.fi/user/newr">here</a> to register if you don't already have an account.
</p>

